query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(CASE WHEN sampleData IS NULL OR sampleData = '[]' OR sampleData = 'null' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as missing_sampleData,
  SUM(CASE WHEN sourceUrl IS NULL OR sourceUrl = '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as missing_sourceUrl,
  SUM(CASE WHEN screenshotUrls IS NULL OR screenshotUrls = '[]' OR screenshotUrls = 'null' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as missing_screenshots,
  SUM(CASE WHEN threatActor IS NULL OR threatActor = '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as missing_threatActor,
  SUM(CASE WHEN leakPrice IS NULL OR leakPrice = '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as missing_price,
  SUM(CASE WHEN breachMethod IS NULL OR breachMethod = '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as missing_breachMethod,
  SUM(CASE WHEN breachMethodAr IS NULL OR breachMethodAr = '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as missing_breachMethodAr,
  SUM(CASE WHEN sourcePlatform IS NULL OR sourcePlatform = '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as missing_sourcePlatform
FROM leaks
